def evaluating(x):
    if x <50 :
        return 'A'
    elif x<=100 :
        return 'B'
    elif x<=150 :
        return 'C'
    else :
        return 'D'
# A <= 50 15평
# B <=100 30평
# C <=150 45평
# D >150  45평 이상

yyyy=2006
DATA=pd.DataFrame()

while(yyyy<2022) : 
    FILE = './RealEstate/Seoul_Trading/{year}.csv'.format(year=yyyy)
    data = pd.read_csv(FILE,encoding='utf-8', index_col=False)
    data = data.drop(index =data.index[0:14])
    for idx in range(0, data.columns.size):
        data.rename(columns = {data.columns[idx]:data.iloc[0].values[idx]},inplace =True)
    data = data.drop(index =data.index[0:1])
    data['시'] = data.시군구.str.split().str[0]
    data['구'] = data.시군구.str.split().str[1]
    data['동'] = data.시군구.str.split().str[2]
    data['계약년월'] = data['계약년월'].astype(str)
    data['계약 년'] = data.계약년월.str[:4]
    data['계약 월'] = data.계약년월.str[4:]
    data = data.drop(columns=['해제사유발생일','시군구','계약일'])
    data= data[['시', '구', '동', '계약 년', '계약 월', '본번', '부번', '단지명', '전용면적(㎡)','층', '건축년도', '거래금액(만원)', '도로명']]
    data= data.sort_values(by=['계약 월'],ascending=True)
    data= data.reset_index(drop=True)

    data['전용면적(㎡)'] = data['전용면적(㎡)'].astype(float)
    data['거래금액(만원)'] = data['거래금액(만원)'].str.replace(",","").astype(int)


    data['area'] = data['전용면적(㎡)'].apply(evaluating)
    data['price_per_area'] = data['거래금액(만원)']/data['전용면적(㎡)']
    df = data[col_to_use].groupby(by=['구','area']).mean()

    index = [(yyyy,yyyy),('거래금액(만원)','price_per_area')]
    index =pd.MultiIndex.from_arrays(index)
    df.columns = index
    df = df.unstack()
    if(yyyy==2006):
        DATA = df
    else :
        DATA=pd.concat([DATA,df],axis=1)
    yyyy+=1
    
DATA

In [42]:
yyyy=2006
while(yyyy<2022):
    FILE = './RealEstate/Seoul_Trading/{year}.csv'.format(year=yyyy)
    data = pd.read_csv(FILE,encoding='utf-8', index_col=False)
    data = data.drop(index =data.index[0:14])
    for idx in range(0, data.columns.size):
        data.rename(columns = {data.columns[idx]:data.iloc[0].values[idx]},inplace =True)
    data = data.drop(index =data.index[0:1])
    data['시'] = data.시군구.str.split().str[0]
    data['구'] = data.시군구.str.split().str[1]
    data['동'] = data.시군구.str.split().str[2]
    data['계약년월'] = data['계약년월'].astype(str)
    data['계약 년'] = data.계약년월.str[:4]
    data['계약 월'] = data.계약년월.str[4:]
    data = data.drop(columns=['해제사유발생일','시군구','계약일'])
    data= data[['시', '구', '동', '계약 년', '계약 월', '본번', '부번', '단지명', '전용면적(㎡)','층', '건축년도', '거래금액(만원)', '도로명']]
    data= data.sort_values(by=['계약 월'],ascending=True)
    data= data.reset_index(drop=True)

    data['전용면적(㎡)'] = data['전용면적(㎡)'].astype(float)
    data['거래금액(만원)'] = data['거래금액(만원)'].str.replace(",","").astype(int)


    data['area'] = data['전용면적(㎡)'].apply(evaluating)
    data['price_per_area'] = data['거래금액(만원)']/data['전용면적(㎡)']

    df = data[col_to_use]
    index = [(yyyy,)*len(data),tuple(x for x in range(len(data))) ]
    index =pd.MultiIndex.from_arrays(index)
    #df.drop_index(drop=True,inplac=True)
    df.set_index(index)
    df.columns = col_to_use
    
    
    if(yyyy==2006):
        DATA = df
    else :
        DATA=pd.concat([DATA,df],axis=0)
    yyyy+=1

def autolabel(axes,df):
    y = ['A','B','C','D']
    newval=0
    oldval=0
    i=0
    
    for index in df.index:
        oldval=0
        newval=0
        for col in y :
            oldval+=newval
            newval=df.loc[index][col]
            axes.text(oldval + newval/2 -2, i, round(newval,2))
        i+=1
